body:
Riot put a lot of work into this lore event, and even re-engaged us summoners by showing that lore will have an impact on the actual game.

When the OLD NARRATIVE LEAD said that riot would be seperating the game from lore, everyone bitched and moaned and cried about how that wasn&#039;t good and that the lore SHOULD impact the game.

Now, we are getting exactly that, in an amazing execution, resulting in a champion getting not one, but TWO visual over-hauls, and then giving EVERYONE who has played gangplank during the burning tides a FREE high quality skin.

But nah, people always gotta bitch about something. 

Community: &quot;We want good Lore! We want lore to matter!&quot;

Riot: &quot;Okay! Here is an amazing event, including an actual resolving plotline in which champions grow and develop as characters!&quot;

Ungrateful Chillens: &quot;Fuk u rito gimme bak gangplank we dnt wnt no lore fuk u!&quot;

:X
